    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“Come in with me,” she urges the simple. To those who lack good judgment, she says, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“Come in with me,” she urges the simple. To those who lack good judgment, she says,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“Come, eat my food, and drink the wine I have mixed. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“Come, eat my food, and drink the wine I have mixed."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Leave your simple ways behind, and begin to live; learn to use good judgment.” "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Leave your simple ways behind, and begin to live; learn to use good judgment.”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Anyone who rebukes a mocker will get an insult in return. Anyone who corrects the wicked will get hurt. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Anyone who rebukes a mocker will get an insult in return. Anyone who corrects the wicked will get hurt."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "So don’t bother correcting mockers; they will only hate you. But correct the wise, and they will love you. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "So don’t bother correcting mockers; they will only hate you. But correct the wise, and they will love you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Instruct the wise, and they will be even wiser. Teach the righteous, and they will learn even more. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Instruct the wise, and they will be even wiser. Teach the righteous, and they will learn even more."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Fear of the Lord is the foundation of wisdom. Knowledge of the Holy One results in good judgment. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Fear of the Lord is the foundation of wisdom. Knowledge of the Holy One results in good judgment."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Wisdom will multiply your days and add years to your life. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Wisdom will multiply your days and add years to your life."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "If you become wise, you will be the one to benefit. If you scorn wisdom, you will be the one to suffer. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "If you become wise, you will be the one to benefit. If you scorn wisdom, you will be the one to suffer."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
